 #Resample by month (sum/mean)
monthly_production = data['units_produced'].resample('M').sum()
monthly_defects = data['defects_found'].resample('M').mean()

# Plot
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 6))
monthly_production.plot(label='Units Produced', ax=ax)
monthly_defects.plot(label='Avg Defects', secondary_y=True, ax=ax)

plt.grid(True)
